# Description
# -----------
#
#  Completion script for symfony console (https://github.com/symfony/Console).
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Authors
# -------
#
#  * loranger (https://github.com/loranger)
#  * Yohan Tamb√® (https://github.com/Cronos87)
